children.value: I've been teaching full stack web development for 3 years now, and I have quite a few thoughts to share about this topic.

This article will talk about my experiences with students, trying to reach students, planning lessons. It will also cover things from the teachers perspective - thigns like avoiding burnout, not taking stress home, etc.
